window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>For years, the ancient alien AI known as Skippy (the Magnificent, don’t forget that part) has been able to do one impossible thing after another. What is his secret? It’s simple: 100 percent Grade-A extreme awesomeness. And also because he had never been faced with an opponent of equal power. Until now.</p> <p>This time, he might need a little help from a band of filthy monkeys.</p>"; 
